            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-fde433c6-40e7-400e-a0f6-fd40fc17e109">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-fde433c6-40e7-400e-a0f6-fd40fc17e109" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-29/debates/4f9b1421-eee6-4619-bec1-54f3f9993a57/MinisterialSalariesAndTransport#contribution-fde433c6-40e7-400e-a0f6-fd40fc17e109">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">While expressing my acknowledgments of the kindly thought manifested by the hon. Gentleman, it is not proposed at the present time to change the arrangements made when the Government was formed.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-fde433c6-40e7-400e-a0f6-fd40fc17e109" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
