<p class="">Is my right hon. Friend aware that the opinion is widely held in this House and in the country that a person in receipt of an income of £4,000 a year is capable of providing himself with a motor car without any charge on public funds?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
