<p class="">I have made certain arrangements which are being laboriously carried out, but it is easier to see these things in theory than to carry them out in practice. I propose to persevere on the exact basis which I set forth when we took office six months ago.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
